parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Brake Line Chafing and Brake Fluid Loss
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The chafing of the brake line against the air cleaner housing can cause a complete brake fluid loss, leading to a loss of braking ability, which can result in accidents or injuries.
